I'm sure you already know this and I know some comment from a random stranger on the internet isn't going to change your behavior, but you really shouldn't do speedballs.

The high just isn't worth the absolute ***hell*** you are putting your heart and the rest of your body through.  I'm all for getting fucked up, but I also think harm reduction is important and when you start mixing uppers and downers (especially IV) you are *greatly* increasing your risk for countless unwanted complications.  

Enjoy yourself tonight, but really, I would try to not make it a habit to IV speedballs.  It's basically a death wish.
